des:
The Skill primarily focuses on providing some really inspiring and motivating quotes of several important personalities of the world.
The Skill uses no account creation nor does it does any sort of hardware.

Simple invoke the skill using 'Alexa, Open Inspirational Quotes' and you are good to go.
